rows.name:
I was raising this pet Pilehorn Rhino
Beetle I found in an old factory, but
it died recently...

rows.label: tlk45100152_04_msg0002
rows.name:
So now I'm raising this Tender Shark
I caught at the Nopon Pioneers' Spring!

rows.label: tlk45100152_04_msg0003
rows.name:
He's a lovely little guy. Looks after all
the other fish for me. As long as there's
seaweed, I don't even have to feed him!
